document.title: Corpus Gysseling Online
document.intro: The corpus Gysseling presented here is a collection of all thirteen-century sources that were used for the Early Middle-Dutch Dictionary. This is a digital release with annotations of word class and lemma's of the thirteenth century material from the Corpus of Middel-Dutch texts (until ... Displays sentences of fragments from the corpus.
